### Local-only safety checks
- Frontmatter is visible in the local file but never sent as body content.
- Body pushes use Notion Markdown updates with stale-write checks.
- Property and metadata pushes can proceed independently from remote body edits.
- Unknown-block deletion requires explicit destructive intent.
- Roughdraft review markers are refused by default so local review state does not leak into Notion.
